Welcome!
Amazing Wedding Ceremonies
Happen Here!

How beautiful is the day that is touched by love!

Larry James performs the most "romantic" wedding ceremony you will find anywhere! He is one of Arizona's leading full-time, interfaith and non-denominational wedding officiants. Larry's experience in performing amazing romantic wedding ceremonies is unsurpassed!

No two weddings are the same. No two couples are the same. Your wedding is unique, your ceremony should be too. Why? Because "the ceremony" IS the wedding!

So. . . if you are looking for a customized, "romantic" wedding ceremony with some refreshing words that will capture the attention of your guests; one that is truly different from the ordinary, traditional wedding ceremony, you've come to the right place. OR... if you are looking to save $$$ and want a quick, romantic ceremony the "Kiss 'n Go" ceremony is a great alternative to a court house wedding by a Justice of the Peace. Your wedding is your very romantic day! We want to help you create a day uniquely your own and make it a memorable event.

After one of Larry's recent weddings, a guest was heard to say, "Larry's romantic wedding ceremony was a gift to my ears!" Larry James has been called "The Concierge of Romantic Celebrations!"

We believe that we are better than your other choices for wedding ministers/officiants! Why? Our former wedding clients say so! Check out some of our "Rave Reviews" and visit the wedding gallery! Call Larry James for a no-cost, no-obligation, get acquainted session. 480-205-3694

Check Larry's Availabilty!

Larry James. . . magically making every wedding special, and never lacking in class or originality! Every wedding ceremony is different giving every couple the chance to have what they've always dreamed of. Your personal choices are Larry's highest priority! Larry's "romantic" wedding ceremony is economically irresistible!

Fee Quote Site Map

Larry's "Kiss 'n Go®" Ceremony! For those just want to get married and want to skip the fanfare and expense of a large wedding at a Hotel or Resort! If you are looking to save $$$ and want a quick, romantic ceremony the "Kiss 'n Go" ceremony is a great alternative to a court house wedding by a Justice of the Peace. (This ceremony has been so successful that it has been extended to all year!)

We will help you make your wedding experience everything you want it to be. Your ceremony will be uniquely yours; custom designed with romantic elegance and impeccable attention to detail; one that will be a cherished memory for a lifetime.

Your wedding ceremony can be as solemn and dignified or as fun and creative as you want it. You always have the last word in creating your very special ceremony.

Larry James is listed on the "Preferred Vendors" list of many of the Greater Phoenix area's finest resorts and wedding venues! He is one of the busiest, most creative and unique wedding officiants in the Greater Phoenix area.


Call Larry James
480-205-3694
Planning your wedding in Arizona and you live in another state? Larry James is an expert at helping with all of the details of your Destination Wedding. Larry does lots of Destination Weddings and will do everything possible to make your wedding as stress-free as possible! Need referrals to Wedding Consultants, DJs, Photographers, etc., give him a call.

Our purpose is to assist you with all aspects of your wedding. You will find lots of innovative and inspiring ideas that will help with your planning, etc., including a very special ceremony performed by Larry James. He is an ordained non-denominational Wedding Officiant, professional speaker, nationally recognized relationship coach and author of three relationship books.

Our wedding and relationship articles menu will assist you in your relationships and more. Browse our book store featuring a wide selection of books about weddings and relationships. You'll also find a special links page to many other wedding sites and wedding related items.

Services Provided

Weddings • Ceremonies: Religious, Non-Religious, Interfaith, Interdenominational, Intercultural, Same-Faith, Traditional and Non-traditional, Theme Weddings (50's, Halloween, Humorous, etc., by request) • Renewal & Reaffirmation of Vows • LBGT Weddings • Pre-marital & Post-marital Coaching • Destination Weddings • Commitment Ceremonies • Grand Canyon Weddings • Weddings at Sandals Resorts

Larry James is an ordained non-denominational Wedding Officiant who is a Christian however he never pushes his Spiritual beliefs on anyone. He honors and respects all beliefs and traditions - religious, spiritual, non-religious, or secular. Your ceremony will be what you want it to be!

Premarital coaching is available and is not required. Premarital coaching is not necessarily only for couples experiencing relationship problems, but often is a wise idea to learn more about the reality of marriage.

His ceremony was also super engaging... not boring. Many people came up to us and told us how beautiful our ceremony was. HIGHLY recommend Larry! ~ Lizzy Dietrich & Jenna Lowry
